## **sparklines: gtExtras method**

### Data Preparation


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report <- coffeechain %>%
  mutate(Year = year(Date)) %>%
  filter(Year == "2013") %>%
  mutate (Month = month(Date, 
                        label = TRUE, 
                        abbr = TRUE)) %>%
  group_by(Product, Month) %>%
  summarise(Sales = sum(Sales)) %>%
  ungroup()
```
:::


::: callout-important
A requirement of gtExtras function: data.frame must be passed with list columns. Thus, the report data.frame must be converted into list columns.
:::

Convert Data Frame into List Columns


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report %>%
  group_by(Product) %>%
  summarize('Monthly Sales' = list(Sales), 
            .groups = "drop")
```

