### **Combining bullet chart and sparklines**

Bullet Chart


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
bullet <- coffeechain %>%
  filter(Date >= "2013-01-01") %>%
  group_by(`Product`) %>%
  summarise(`Target` = sum(`Budget Sales`),
            `Actual` = sum(`Sales`)) %>%
  ungroup() 
```
:::


Join data


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sales_data = sales_data %>%
  left_join(bullet)
```
